column1: Table 5: Revisions to official long-term international immigration, emigration and net migration estimates for YE September 2023 to YE June 2024 [definitions 2, 3, 4]
Notes and definitions are referred to in this table. The text for these can be found in the corresponding worksheets.
Some shorthand is used in this table, P = provisional, R = revised, YE = Year Ending and EU = European Union.
